profile:
10 years architectural design.  Registered with the Ministry of Municipal Affairs for small buildings up to 3 storeys and 6500 square feet.  Working drawings for your project in Muskoka and Parry Sound.

Just like you, we love scenic hikes, dinner with friends and cozy campfires.  
We are also partners with a passion for bridging creative planning

 & quality construction.

Our Mission is to DRAW YOUR VISION of home, cottage  or workspace so you can clearly communicate your plans to tradespeople, officials and others.

At the end of the day, we want you to have the structures you need to live your life best!
